## PR Workflow

1. Develop on a feature branch (never directly on main/master)
2. Write or update specs alongside code — same PR
3. Commit frequently with descriptive messages
4. Push early and create a draft PR
5. Self-review diff before marking ready
6. Never let specs and code diverge — update PRODUCT.md/TECH.md when implementation changes

---

## Parallelization Guidelines

For every non-trivial feature, actively evaluate:
- Can research and implementation be split into parallel agents?
- Can independent modules be implemented simultaneously in separate worktrees?
- Can tests be written in parallel with implementation?

